The Crypt spider is a small spider found in the tunnels of the Barrows and the Chaos Tunnels. They tend to hit extremely low, and are not a threat, unless your combat stats are poor. Food may be advised, as they are aggressive to all players for a period of time.

These are one of the most killed monster in Barrows for the kill count. They are rarely killed for anything else, seeing as how they are in inconvenient places to kill and are generally weak.
